4:27.846Z","team_member_agreed_on_going_public_at":null,"comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"## Summary:\n Assessor observed that password reset function generates only alphanumeric passwords that is passwords don't contain any special characters \nAlso User can set old password as new password.\n\n## Steps To Reproduce:\n\nGoto https://mycontract.mtn.co.za/landing/landing.htm\nClick forget password link\nselect email radio button and enter user ID\npress submit \n\n*Application will send email with week password*\n\nupon entering temporary password application ask user to set new password\nhere user can enter his immediate used password\n\n\n## Supporting Material/References:\n\nhttps://www.owasp.org/index.php/Authentication_Cheat_Sheet\nhttps://www.owasp.org/index.php/Top_10-2017_A3-Sensitive_Data_Exposure\n\nRemediation:\nApplication should generate secure passwords thats password should contain alphanumeric characters as well as special characters \nApplication should not allow user to set previously used 5 password as new password\n\n## Impact\n\n## Impact \nBrute force attack can be carried out on the password based authentication mechanism","weakness":{"id":92,"name":"Weak Password Recovery Mechanism for Forgotten Password"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":669582,"file_name":"password_reset_not_secure.jpg","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/6EDHq1DprECxrUEo5DrTt2h8?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22password_reset_not_secure.jpg%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27password_reset_not_secure.jpg\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fjpeg\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQYTWDFFHY%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T090128Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECgaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIQC